episodes.title: The TERRIFYING Last Minutes of Christian Music Singer Keith Green
episodes.description:
On July 28, 1982, American Christian music singer Keith Green, along with his 3-year-old son and 2-year-old daughter, as well as two of his friends and their six children, boarded a 7-seat Cessna 414 (registration number N110VM) for a sightseeing trip around the ranch. However, just a few minutes after takeoff, tragedy struck.
